Class CustomProperty

    • com.siemens.sbom.standardbom.model.CustomProperty

    The names of custom properties that we support in CycloneDX Components as per the Siemens Property Taxonomy for CycloneDX.

      • VCS_CLEAN

        public static final String VCS_CLEAN
        A flag (true or false) indicating whether the Git workspace was clean when the SBOM was created, i.e. all changes had been committed.

        Used on SBOM level, when describing the component for which the SBOM is created.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • VCS_REVISION

        public static final String VCS_REVISION
        The most recent VCS hash, for example a Git commit hash. Together with VCS_CLEAN, this additional value allows ensuring accurate reproducibility of the SBOM.

        Used on SBOM level, when describing the component for which the SBOM is created.
